data.description: An oasis within the expanse of the high desert. Nestled near the beautiful KRV, this property spans over 18 acres and boasts comprehensive amenities, perfectly suited for accommodating your animals or storing of toys. Constructed in 2004, is financeable and offers a spacious 2,080 square feet. Three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, the home features a large central living area and an eat-in kitchen. A distinct formal dining area adds to its charm. Stepping into the backyard, you'll be captivated. The enclosed yard boasts a built-in pebble tech saltwater pool accompanied by an attached spa, guaranteed to delight everyone. The well water source and whole home solar power system render the maintenance and filling of this pool an affordable endeavor.The two-car garage serves a dual purpose-it is equipped with two separate roll-up doors and two stalls. Additionally, it features a tack room and an expansive extra room. Directly from the property, you can ride your horses/ along endless trail
